title: Host Faves: The Green Children of Woolpit
itunes:title: Host Faves: The Green Children of Woolpit
description:
In 2017 we talked about two children, green in color, who appeared in Suffolk, England in the 12th century,. The green children were written about in the 12th and 13th centuries as fact, but some people today classify as this tale as folklore.
